	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "e932262b-37d4-4675-a84f-5dde6717fe8a",
		"name": "auth",
		"description": "# Authentication API Documentation\n\n## Base URL\n\nAll endpoints are prefixed with: `{{base_url}}`\n\n---\n\n# Admin Registration\n\nRegister a new **admin account**. After registration, an **OTP verification email** will be sent.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/auth/register/admin`\n\n## Request Body\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"fullName\": \"Admin\",\n  \"email\": \"shopmate400@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Shopmate400+\",\n  \"location_data\": {\n    \"city\": \"Lagos\",\n    \"region\": \"Lagos State\",\n    \"country\": \"Nigeria\"\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Note:** `location_data` is optional.\n\n## Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Admin registered successfully. Please verify your email with the OTP sent.\",\n  \"adminId\": \"cmmn9jnm00005n23wdb8f4cbr\",\n  \"email\": \"shopmate400@gmail.com\",\n  \"expiresIn\": \"30 minutes\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Error Response (400)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": [\n    \"Password must contain at least one uppercase letter, one lowercase letter, one number, and one special character (e.g., +=-!@#$%^&*())\"\n  ],\n  \"error\": \"Bad Request\",\n  \"statusCode\": 400\n}\n\n ```\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Email already registered as admin\",\n  \"error\": \"Bad Request\",\n  \"statusCode\": 400\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# User Registration\n\nRegister a new **user account**. An **OTP verification email** will be sent.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/auth/register/user`\n\n## Request Body\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"fullName\": \"Tunji Akande\",\n  \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Akande95+\",\n  \"location_data\": {\n    \"city\": \"Lagos\",\n    \"region\": \"Lagos State\",\n    \"country\": \"Nigeria\"\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Note:** `location_data` is optional.\n\n## Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"User registered successfully. Please verify your email with the OTP sent.\",\n  \"userId\": \"cmmn9exe40002n23wsfuewi42\",\n  \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n  \"expiresIn\": \"30 minutes\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Error Response (400)\n\nSame validation errors as **Admin Registration**, but specific to users.\n\n---\n\n# Login\n\nAuthenticate an **admin or user account**.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/auth/login`\n\n---\n\n## Request Body (Admin)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"email\": \"shopmate400@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Shopmate400+\",\n  \"location_data\": {\n    \"city\": \"Lagos\",\n    \"region\": \"Lagos State\",\n    \"country\": \"Nigeria\"\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Request Body (User)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Akande95+\",\n  \"location_data\": {\n    \"city\": \"Lagos\",\n    \"region\": \"Lagos State\",\n    \"country\": \"Nigeria\"\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Note:** `location_data` is optional.\n\n---\n\n## Success Response (Admin - 200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Login successful\",\n  \"admin\": {\n    \"id\": \"cmmn58hmq0000r43wku4120ph\",\n    \"email\": \"shopmate400@gmail.com\",\n    \"fullName\": \"Admin\",\n    \"role\": \"ADMIN\"\n  },\n  \"sessionId\": \"cmmn776g00000543wt6xglq1r\",\n  \"accountType\": \"admin\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Success Response (User - 200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Login successful\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": \"cmmn9exe40002n23wsfuewi42\",\n    \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n    \"fullName\": \"Tunji Akande\",\n    \"role\": \"USER\"\n  },\n  \"sessionId\": \"cmmn9h0z20004n23wvj3cgi6x\",\n  \"token\": \"sess_522124f943af58170858367dba2e41410f4a00007526eb33d4ddf7880aa7a677\",\n  \"accountType\": \"user\",\n  \"hasCompanyData\": false\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Error Response (401)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Please verify your email first. A new verification code has been sent.\",\n  \"error\": \"Unauthorized\",\n  \"statusCode\": 401\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# Logout\n\nLogs out the currently authenticated **user or admin**.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/auth/logout`\n\n## Authorization\n\nAuthentication token/session is required.\n\n## Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Logged out successfully\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# Verify OTP\n\nVerify the email using the **OTP sent to the user's email**.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/auth/verify-otp`\n\n## Request Body\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"258826\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Email verified successfully\",\n  \"verified\": true\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Error Response (400)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Invalid or expired OTP\",\n  \"error\": \"Bad Request\",\n  \"statusCode\": 400\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# Resend OTP\n\nResends a new **email verification OTP**.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/auth/resend-otp`\n\n## Request Body\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"email\": \"shopmate400@gmail.com\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"A new verification code has been sent to your email\",\n  \"expiresIn\": \"30 minutes\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# Forgot Password\n\nRequest a **password reset link** to be sent to the user's email.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/auth/forgot-password`\n\n## Request Body\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"email\": \"shopmate400@gmail.com\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Password reset instructions have been sent to your email\",\n  \"expiresIn\": \"1 hour\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# Reset Password\n\nReset password using the **reset token from the email**.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/auth/reset-password`\n\n## Request Body\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"oobCode\": \"VPyrrMFuIztjfQv9fVhmGQ95Zt4adXY2eOAvdd3BAH0AAAGc4UlViQ\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"Shopmate400++\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Password has been reset successfully. You can now log in with your new password.\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n## Error Response (400)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Invalid reset link. Please request a new one.\",\n  \"error\": \"Bad Request\",\n  \"statusCode\": 400\n}\n\n ```\n\n---",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
